USD_INSTALL_ROOT = path to USD folder data

----------------------------------
PYTHONPATH = USD_INSTALL_ROOT/lib/python
PATH = USD_INSTALL_ROOT/bin, USD_INSTALL_ROOT/lib/bin

Making USDVIEW work in Windows 10

----------------------------------
env variables to set in the usdviewew/cmd fle
@set BINP=%~dp0
@set LIBP=%~dp0..\lib
@set PYP=%~dp0..\lib\python
@set PATH=%PATH%;%BINP%;%LIBP%
@set PYTHONPATH=%PYTHONPATH%;%PYP%
@python “%~dp0usdview” %*

